title: Texas hurricane cocktail
ingredients: ['1 cupful crushed ice', '2 tablespoons rum', '2 tablespoons coconut rum', '2 tablespoons vodka', '2 tablespoons gin', '2 tablespoons triple sec (orange flavoured liqueur)', '4 tablespoons orange juice', '2 tablespoons pineapple juice', '2 tablespoons grenadine syrup', '2 tablespoons 151 proof rum', '1 orange slice', '1 lime slice', '1 cocktail cherry']
